snippet.title: Behind the Beyond trailer
snippet.description:
Behind the Beyond is a point & click adventure game based on Hungarian folklore. 
The game is currently in development by Sugarpunch Games.

Check out the DEMO on Steam and itch.io:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1148310/Behind_the_Beyond/
https://sugarpunch-games.itch.io/behind-the-beyond

Follow us:
https://behindthebeyond.com/
https://twitter.com/BehindTheBeyond
https://www.facebook.com/BehindTheBeyond
https://www.instagram.com/sugarpunchgames

TRAILER CREDITS
Art: Katalin Rabel, Marton Adam Marton, VikusVikus.
Music: Kerekes Band.
Voices: Howard Collis, Tom Hounsham, Kev Summers, Gary Woodlock, Chris Dale, Jane O'Sullivan, Adrienne Cox.
